          Lecciones::create([
              'modulo_id'=>3,
              'numero' =>2,
              'nombre'=>'EJEMPLO DE PREGUNTAS',
              'descripcion'=>'<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.44;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:10pt;text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:Calibri;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;">Ejemplo 1.</span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.44;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:10pt;text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:Calibri;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;">Lea las descripciones de la columna de la izquierda y las palabras de la columna de la derecha. ¿Cuál palabra concuerda con la descripción de cada frase en la izquierda? En este caso, simplemente trace una línea uniendo las opciones correctas.</span></p><div dir="ltr" style="margin-left:-5.4pt;"><table style="border:none;border-collapse:collapse"><colgroup><col width="312"><col width="222"></colgroup><tbody><tr style="height:45pt"><td style="border-left:solid #000000 0.5pt;border-right:solid #000000 0.5pt;border-bottom:solid #000000 0.5pt;border-top:solid #000000 0.5pt;vertical-align:top;background-color:#ffffff;padding:0pt 5.4pt 0pt 5.4pt;"><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.7999999999999998;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:Calibri;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;">1. &nbsp;&nbsp;You can take a lot of pictures with it. &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.7999999999999998;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:Calibri;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;">2. &nbsp;&nbsp;People can watch and listen to it.</span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.7999999999999998;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:Calibri;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;">3. &nbsp;&nbsp;People can read with it at night.</span></p></td><td style="border-left:solid #000000 0.5pt;border-right:solid #000000 0.5pt;border-bottom:solid #000000 0.5pt;border-top:solid #000000 0.5pt;vertical-align:top;background-color:#00b0f0;padding:0pt 5.4pt 0pt 5.4pt;"><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:Calibri;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;">A. &nbsp;lamp </span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:Calibri;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;">B. &nbsp;television </span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:Calibri;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;">C. &nbsp;door </span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:Calibri;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weigh